      "side": 1,
      "message": "There\u0027s some risk in marshaling members like this that the spec says are ignored in some cases\nsuch as in this case \"is ignored if the pipeline does not include a tessellation control shader stage and tessellation evaluation shader stage\".\nAn app could have garbage here that may lead to a crash due to invalid access.",
